title: ProviderRow primaryWindows uses truthy visible; ExpandedView uses !== false
updated_at: "2026-07-15T04:40:48Z"
---
## Problem
`primaryWindows` requires `w.visible && w.role === "primary"` (truthy `visible`). ExpandedView uses `w.visible !== false`, which is more defensive if `visible` is missing. Inconsistent filtering could hide windows in ProviderRow if a parser forgets `visible`.

## Location
contents/ui/ProviderRow.qml (primaryWindows)

## Suggested fix
Align with `visible !== false` and the primary-role fallback used in ExpandedView/main compact.

